      • onActivityCreated

        void onActivityCreated(android.os.Bundle savedInstanceState)
        Called when the fragment's activity has been created. Creates a MrqContentListAdapter using onCreateContentAdapter() and passes the result to setListAdapter(ListAdapter). It initializes MrqContentListLoader by calling onInitContentLoader();
        Parameters:
        savedInstanceState - If the fragment is being re-created from a previous saved state, this is the state.

      • onCreateContentAdapter

        Returns:
        The adaptor

      • onInitContentLoader

        void onInitContentLoader()
        Called by onActivityCreated(Bundle) to initialize the MrqContentLoader. Calls LoaderManager.initLoader(int, Bundle, LoaderManager.LoaderCallbacks) with id MRQ_CONTENT_LOADER_ID and this as LoaderManager.LoaderCallbacks.

      • onListItemClick

        void onListItemClick(android.widget.ListView l,
                   android.view.View v,
                   int position,
                   long id)
        Called by ListView when content is clicked. Tracks a click by calling MrqSdk.trackContentClick(Context, MrqContent) Uses AdapterView.getItemAtPosition(int) to find MrqContent. Ignores items that are not MrqContent. Calls onContentClick(ListView, MrqContentView) with the selected MrqContentView
        Parameters:
        l - The ListView where the click happened
        v - The view that was clicked within the ListView
        position - The position of the view in the list
        id - The row id of the item that was clicked

      • onContentClick

        void onContentClick(android.widget.ListView l,
                  MrqContentView v)
        Called by onListItemClick(ListView, View, int, long) when content is clicked. Loads MrqContent.getCreativeUrl() ()} in a browser. Uses onListItemClick(ListView, View, int, long) to find MrqContent. Ignores items that are not MrqContent. Override this method to implement deep links.
        Parameters:
        l - The ListView where the click happened
        v - The MrqContentView that was clicked within the ListView
